  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=736 height=61 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Pathogen X\" is an immersive first-person survival horror game where you step into the shoes of BRCI special agent Aiden Clark. Embark on a perilous mission to an underground laboratory to thwart a biological catastrophe and secure a sample of the deadly Pathogen X. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biological Threat:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a myriad of nightmarish mutations spawned by Pathogen X, fighting to survive in an environment teeming with lethal mutants that relentlessly hunt you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/a469e1b3b45c779b9e6391a9aea7d727.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/a469e1b3b45c779b9e6391a9aea7d727.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/a469e1b3b45c779b9e6391a9aea7d727.mp4?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperation and Guidance:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your mission, Special Agent Maya Ackerman will assist you via satellite communication, providing vital updates and helping you navigate complex challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horror Atmosphere:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's chilling atmosphere and detailed environments amplify the dread of the underground laboratory, where every step could be your last. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/d6d4c06114ea8c3a02f38bcb14385d12.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=615 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/d6d4c06114ea8c3a02f38bcb14385d12.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and wield an array of weapons scattered throughout the underground complex to combat the horrifying mutants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadly and Terrifying Enemies:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a diverse range of enemies, each with unique traits and abilities. From the mindlessly aggressive to the incredibly powerful and cunning, you'll need to devise strategies to defeat them all. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/68ca097eaccdcde16eee6532814d57bc.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/68ca097eaccdcde16eee6532814d57bc.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/68ca097eaccdcde16eee6532814d57bc.mp4?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breathtaking Graphics:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features stunning visuals that plunge you into the grim world of the underground lab with remarkable detail and realism. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Puzzles:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the lab's complexities by using your intuition. Whether shooting a lock or breaking boards to clear a path, these elements add depth and mystery to the gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/f68bd4ef7e609cc5e2b48501af52f903.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=615 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/f68bd4ef7e609cc5e2b48501af52f903.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings and Extra Modes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Pathogen X\" offers several endings influenced by your actions and decisions, though they don't alter the ultimate conclusion. Upon completion, additional modes and quests become available, enriching the gaming experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Pathogen X\" features a dynamic soundtrack tailored for intense firefights. Energetic tunes heighten the tension during battles, while the sound effects of weapons and enemies merge with the music to create an exhilarating audio experience that enhances the game's action and atmosphere. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=736 height=61 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/e2a276a3cc848b6379538baaa6987a67.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=615 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/e2a276a3cc848b6379538baaa6987a67.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=736 height=61 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Pathogen X\" is an immersive first-person survival horror game where you step into the shoes of BRCI special agent Aiden Clark. Embark on a perilous mission to an underground laboratory to thwart a biological catastrophe and secure a sample of the deadly Pathogen X. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biological Threat:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a myriad of nightmarish mutations spawned by Pathogen X, fighting to survive in an environment teeming with lethal mutants that relentlessly hunt you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/a469e1b3b45c779b9e6391a9aea7d727.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/a469e1b3b45c779b9e6391a9aea7d727.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/a469e1b3b45c779b9e6391a9aea7d727.mp4?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperation and Guidance:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your mission, Special Agent Maya Ackerman will assist you via satellite communication, providing vital updates and helping you navigate complex challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horror Atmosphere:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's chilling atmosphere and detailed environments amplify the dread of the underground laboratory, where every step could be your last. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/d6d4c06114ea8c3a02f38bcb14385d12.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=615 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/d6d4c06114ea8c3a02f38bcb14385d12.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and wield an array of weapons scattered throughout the underground complex to combat the horrifying mutants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadly and Terrifying Enemies:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a diverse range of enemies, each with unique traits and abilities. From the mindlessly aggressive to the incredibly powerful and cunning, you'll need to devise strategies to defeat them all. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/68ca097eaccdcde16eee6532814d57bc.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/68ca097eaccdcde16eee6532814d57bc.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/68ca097eaccdcde16eee6532814d57bc.mp4?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breathtaking Graphics:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features stunning visuals that plunge you into the grim world of the underground lab with remarkable detail and realism. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Puzzles:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the lab's complexities by using your intuition. Whether shooting a lock or breaking boards to clear a path, these elements add depth and mystery to the gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/f68bd4ef7e609cc5e2b48501af52f903.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=615 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/f68bd4ef7e609cc5e2b48501af52f903.webm?t=1729327374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings and Extra Modes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Pathogen X\" offers several endings influenced by your actions and decisions, though they don't alter the ultimate conclusion. Upon completion, additional modes and quests become available, enriching the gaming experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Pathogen X\" features a dynamic soundtrack tailored for intense firefights. Energetic tunes heighten the tension during battles, while the sound effects of weapons and enemies merge with the music to create an exhilarating audio experience that enhances the game's action and atmosphere. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508980/extras/2241fa308f6d233ac74363c46e07771c.poster.avif?t=1729327374\" width=736 height=61 ><source src=\"https:/